thread.title: Chris

author: Chris
title: Chris
text:
I don't have a "main stream" phone (ZTE Blade V Plus) so I was impressed that Mobile Mate even had ANY cases in stock that would fit it. Not only did they have them (no one else did), they had the style I was after (wallet case) in several colours.
Not having heard of Mobile Mate before, I first researched them on Whirlpool as I'm paranoid about online shopping with companies I don't know. Reviews on Whirlpool were positive so I placed the order.
The phone case was dispatched the same day and I received my order IN PERTH only 2 days later.
The case is great quality and fits the phone perfectly!
Couldn't be happier.
